name: LiFE (Logical iOS Forensics Examiner)
tagline: LiFE (Logical iOS Forensics Examiner): An open source iOS backup forensics examination tool
body: LiFE (Logical iOS Forensics Examiner), an open source iOS backup forensics examination tool. This tool helps both researchers and practitioners alike in both understanding the backup structures of iOS devices and forensically examining iOS backups.
